718536f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 106th Street (West)
718536f-a.text:
Central Park West, at West 106th Street. Also shown is West 106th Street, west from and including Central Park West. Building shown on the left, is the General Memorial Hospital. Note the Ninth Ave., Elevated on
Columbus Ave.
December 8, 1916.
E. Mason.
718536f-a.folder: Central Park West & 106th Street (West), Manhattan, NY

718539f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 106th Street
718539f-a.text:
Central Parl West, west side, from 106th to 107th Streets. In the left may be seen a pontion of the General Memorial Hospital. Note the condition of the street, due to excavation work on the
Eighth Avenue subway.
July 10, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

718540f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 106th Street
718540f-a.text:
Central Park West, 107th to 106th Streets. (Before R'.
construction).
